us</li>\n      <li>Maximum cashout or conversion limits</li>\n      <li>Country, age and KYC restrictions</li>\n    </ul>\n    <p class=\"tcs-text\">\n      If there is any difference between the information shown on TopCasinoScout and the casino\u2019s own\n      bonus page, <strong>the casino\u2019s terms always take precedence</strong>.\n    </p>\n\n    <!-- Section 3 -->\n    <h3 class=\"tcs-heading-lg\">3. How We Monitor & Update Bonus Data</h3>\n    <p class=\"tcs-text\">\n      TopCasinoScout uses a combination of manual checks, operator communication and internal tools to\n      keep bonus data as accurate as possible. Our editorial team:\n    </p>\n    <ul class=\"tcs-list\">\n      <li>Reviews key bonus pages and rankings on a regular schedule</li>\n      <li>Updates major welcome offers and deposit bonuses when notified by partners</li>\n      <li>Performs spot checks on popular casinos and high-traffic pages</li>\n      <li>Removes or downgrades casinos that repeatedly provide misleading bonus information</li>\n    </ul>\n    <p class=\"tcs-text\">\n      You can learn more about how we evaluate bonuses and casinos in our\n      <a href=\"/how-we-rate\" style=\"color:#ffcc33;\">How We Rate</a> guide and\n      <a href=\"/editorial-policy\" style=\"color:#ffcc33;\">Editorial Policy</a>.\n    </p>\n\n    <!-- Section 4 -->\n    <h3 class=\"tcs-heading-lg\">4. No Guarantee of Eligibility or Acceptance</h3>\n    <p class=\"tcs-text\">\n      The presence of a bonus or casino offer on TopCasinoScout does not guarantee that:\n    </p>\n    <ul class=\"tcs-list\">\n      <li>You will be eligible for the promotion</li>\n      <li>Your account or documents will be accepted by the casino</li>\n      <li>Your deposit or withdrawal will be processed successfully</li>\n      <li>You are legally allowed to gamble in your jurisdiction</li>\n    </ul>\n    <p class=\"tcs-text\">\n      It is your responsibility to ensure that <strong>online gambling is legal for you</strong> and that you\n      meet all age, identity and location requirements before playing.\n    </p>\n\n    <!-- Section 5 -->\n    <h3 class=\"tcs-heading-lg\">5. Player Feedback & Error Reporting</h3>\n    <p class=\"tcs-text\">\n      If you spot a bonus that is incorrect, expired, or does not match what you see on the casino\u2019s website,\n      we want to know. Your feedback helps us keep the site more accurate for everyone.\n    </p>\n    <p class=\"tcs-text\">\n      You can report issues or discrepancies via our\n      <a href=\"/contact-us\" style=\"color:#ffcc33;\">Contact Us</a> page. In more serious\n      cases involving unfair treatment, missing payouts or misleading terms, you may also reference our\n      <a href=\"/complaints-transparency-report\" style=\"color:#ffcc33;\">\n        Complaints & Transparency Report\n      </a>.\n    </p>\n\n    <!-- Section 6 -->\n    <h3 class=\"tcs-heading-lg\">6. Not Financial or Legal Advice</h3>\n    <p class=\"tcs-text\">\n      All content on TopCasinoScout is provided for information and entertainment purposes only. It should\n      not be considered financial, legal or professional advice. We encourage all users to gamble responsibly,\n      never chase losses, and only play with money they can afford to lose.\n    </p>\n    <p class=\"tcs-text\">\n      For support and safer gambling tools, please visit our\n      <a href=\"/responsible-gambling\" style=\"color:#ffcc33;\">Responsible Gambling</a> page.\n    </p>\n\n    <p class=\"tcs-text-muted\" style=\"margin-top:30px;\">\n      Last updated: <?php echo date('F j, Y'); ?>\n    </p>\n\n  </div>\n</section>";
